<plot>On April 16th, 1945 one destroyer defied all odds in a battle that went down in history. Laffey Men follows a man on his journey to find the truth about what happened to his father in WWII. Along the way, he hears the stories of 4 other men besides his father who survived a Kamikaze attack that no one should have survived.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?318038</url></doc>
